  "texts": [
    "For both language pairs, low-activity projects see modest increases in contribution volume, while high-activity projects witness substantial growth.",
    "The gap between maintenance and code development, as well as that between commits with and without new functions, is significantly wider in high-activity projects.",
    "We further test how model improvements affect these patterns by examining GitHub Copilot's June 2022 model upgrade, revealing positive and significant coefficients over and above the main effects.",
    "Together, these findings suggest that, as LLMs enhance their contextual understanding capabilities, they disproportionately augment iterative innovation in context-rich environments, potentially altering the trajectory of collaborative innovation toward exploitation-focused activities in projects with abundant contextual resources.",
    "We contribute to the emerging literature on LLMs and collaborative innovation in several ways."
